Package: secureverse
Title: Umbrella Meta-Package for the secure-r-dev Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ian", "Flores Siaca", , "iflores.siaca@hey.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Umbrella package that loads the seven secure-r-dev
    components (securer, securetools, secureguard, securecontext,
    orchestr, securetrace, securebench) at compatible, pinned versions.
    Also hosts cross-package end-to-end tests that exercise the
    governed-agent, traced-pipeline, retrieval-augmented, and
    benchmarking flows together.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ian-flores/secureverse
